headline: Did Eco-Friendly Devices and Meta Partnership Just Shift Garmin's (GRMN) Investment Narrative?
summary: In recent weeks, Garmin introduced the rugged eTrex Touch GPS handheld navigator and the eco-friendly Descent X30 dive computer, both aimed at outdoor and specialty users, and unveiled a new partnership with Meta to enhance wearable technology capabilities. These launches reflect Garmin's ongoing innovation in high-precision navigation and connected devices, appealing to both adventure enthusiasts and consumers seeking cutting-edge wearable tech.
